item.title: Cyber attack leads to state of emergency
item.description: The cyber attack in the Anhalt-Bitterfeld district had far-reaching effects. All official emails from the last 20 years were deleted, the cash register systems no longer worked and even the alarm systems failed. Feed: https://rss.dw.com/xml/podcast_shift_en
